(190, 1, '2016-05-09 03:24:24', '2016-05-09 03:24:24', '<div class="row">\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img src="../images/newClientSpecial.jpg" alt="before&after">\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<div class="leftAligned" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<h2>New Client Special</h2>\r\n$150 New Client Special. For ALL hair lengths\r\n \r\nYour choice of:\r\n1.unlimited foils\r\n2.All over colour\r\n3.Ombre\r\n \r\nAlso includes a Gloss Toner, Strengthening and moisture Treatment Mask, Precision Style Cut & a Glamorous Blow Dry, Straighten or Curls to finish off your new Amazing Hair.\r\n \r\nCureplex is also available in salon so there is no fear of damaging the condition of your hair.\r\n\r\nAll of our Stylists are all highly experienced Seniors.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[one_half]\r\n<img src="../images/showponyLogo.jpg" alt="showpony logo">\r\n[/one_half]\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n<div class="leftAligned" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<h2>Hair Extensions</h2>\r\nWe use high quality Human Hair extensions. We offer Show Pony and Carla Lawson Hair Extensions.\r\n\r\nTypes of Extensions we are qualified in are\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>I-tip (beaded and Shrinkie)</li>\r\n<li>Skin weft tape</li>\r\n<li>Tape</li>\r\n<li>Hand Tied Weft</li>\r\n<li>clip-ins also available</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCall us on 47756395 to make an appointment for your free consultation for a quote.\r\n\r\n(no quotes will be given over the phone or via PM''s)\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Thick or Extra Long Hair</h2>\r\n$20-$40\r\nPlease note that an extra cost will incur for Thick and Extra Long Hair on some Services. A Quote is always Given before we start any service.\r\n\r\n<h2>Treatments</h2>\r\n$10-$50\r\nWe offer treatments from a basic moisture treatment to the structure complex anti breakage system\r\n\r\n<h2>Pin ups and upstyles</h2>\r\n$50-$90\r\nAll trials are the same price as the acual upstyle as we are proving the same service as on the day.\r\n\r\n<h2>Kids cuts</h2>\r\n$12-25\r\nKids cuts are up to grade 6\r\n\r\n<h2>Curls only</h2>\r\n$30-$70\r\nJust want your Hair Curled? We offer full body curls or just the bottom if you wanted it softer\r\n\r\n<h2>Colour correction remover</h2>\r\n$115-$145\r\nThis includes a dry off Does not include the colour we then have to do 2 days after. Please come in for a consultation for any colour correction so we can give you an estimate.\r\n\r\n<h2>Chemical and Keratin straightening</h2>\r\n$420-$840\r\nConsultation is needed for any quotes for these services. Prices include a style cut and finish\r\n\r\n<h2>Blow dries/ straightening</h2>\r\n$25-$50\r\nIncludes a wash also\r\n\r\n<h2>Facial waxing and tinting</h2>\r\n$10-$40.50\r\nWe offer facial waxing and tinting and also packages for beauty service please ask us for a price on packages\r\n\r\n<h2>Toners</h2>\r\n$20-$95\r\nToners are add one to your service on the day. If you are wanting just a toner as a single service these are under colours.\r\n\r\n<h2>Foils</h2>\r\n$10-$135\r\nOffering panals- full head\r\n\r\n<h2>Ombré/ Balayage services</h2>\r\nA consultation is needed before a quote is given for Ombre/ Balayage.\r\n\r\n<h2>All over glossy colour</h2>\r\n$50-$95\r\nCreated perfectly for each Individual hair type and colour\r\n\r\n<h2>Men''s Cuts</h2>\r\n$25-$35\r\nAll men''s cuts include a wash and finish\r\n\r\n<h2>Ladies Style Cuts</h2>\r\n$40-$80\r\nAll our style cuts include a Wash and finish.\r\n', 'Pricing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '38-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-09 03:24:24', '2016-05-09 03:24:24', '', 38, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2016/05/09/38-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
