going for. So, whether you’re looking for soft and sleek or bold and brilliant, Sarah is the stylist you want by your side.</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Sarah.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">[one_fifth]<img src="../images/stylists/Danielle.jpg" alt="">[/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]<div class="leftAligned">Meet Danielle - Danielle brings a positive upbeat attitude to the salon and is excellent with all hair types and styles for both men and women. She is consistently striving to exceed the customer’s expectations while making them feel comfortable in her chair. Danielle is truly passionate about hair and is always on top of the trends. It’s her personal goal to continue to grow and excel in her craft and to ultimately share all that she learned with her Clients. She stays updated on all the latest trends and places high value on listening and understanding her client’s needs.\r\nShe is extremely passionate about making your hair it’s most fabulous, and prides herself in outstanding customer service. She specializes in colour, and just loves when someone wants a change. Whether you are looking for a great cut and color, or need the perfect look for your wedding, formal, or special occasion, you are sure to fall in love with your hair! Danielle would love to meet with you and she promises to make you love your hair again and again. </div>[/four_fifth_last]</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[four_fifth]<div style="text-align: left;">We would like to introduce our newest Member to our Team, Scarlett!!\r\n\r\nScarlett is very excited to join Karlene and her wonderful team at Rendezvous Hair and Beauty.\r\n\r\nAlong with being a very bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, Scarlett truly loves every aspect of hairdressing, but her speciality lies in Beautiful Blondes.\r\n\r\nScarlett thrives to give guests the best experience and make sure they feel welcome in the salon and not only communicate, but also educate on products and how to look after your hair at home. \r\n\r\nShe looks forward to meeting all of you and welcomes any of her current clients to our prestige boutique salon. \r\n\r\nWelcome Scarlett!</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Scarlett.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">[one_fifth]<img src="../images/stylists/Monique.jpg" alt="">[/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]<div class="leftAligned">We would like to Welcome Monique to our wonderful Team here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty.\r\n\r\nMonique is very passionate about her Clients, she strives to make sure each and every one is extremely well looked after and makes sure that her guests are very pleased with the end result of their hair but can also maintain and upkeep their amazing new look with ease.\r\nMonique understands how important it is to have a connection with your stylist so you are able to come in for a pleasant and easy to communicate appointment, as she knows how scary it can be to find that "perfect" stylist. \r\n\r\nMonique enjoys every aspect of hairdressing there is nothing she won''t strive to achieve "perfection only" when it come to your hair.\r\n\r\nWe welcome all Past clients of Monique''s to come and enjoy your time here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty. </div>[/four_fifth_last]</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[four_fifth]<div style="text-align: left;">The warmest welcomes to Shari!\r\n\r\nShari is a bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, She enjoys to for fill every clients needs and make them feel absolutely beautiful when they leave her chair.\r\n\r\nShari can provide you with up keep information and also easy styling techniques for home. \r\n\r\nShe thrives to give all clients the best experience in salon, help educate you on products and styling with what struggles you may have. \r\n\r\nShari looks forward to meeting new clients and welcomes back any of her past clientele and making you feel special and relaxed\r\nWelcome Scarlett!</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Shari.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Stylists', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-09 04:09:41', '2016-05-09 04:09:41', '', 40, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2016/05/09/40-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(207, 1, '2016-05-09 04:11:50', '2016-05-09 04:11:50', '<div class="row">[one_fifth]<img src="../images/stylists/karlene.jpg" alt="">[/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]<div class="leftAligned">Meet Karlene - Owner and one of the Top Stylists here at Rendezvous hair & Beauty. In the salon, she always strives to create an environment in which her clients are at ease to express themselves and their ideas. Specializing in Hair Extensions, cuts and colours for both men and women. It is Karlene''s goal to help every client find a style that is a true fit for their hair type, and one that the client can easily replicate at home.\r\nOver the years Karlene has had a lot of experience in different areas of the industry, cutting, up styles, re-texturizing and coloring but she continues to advance her skills and keep up to date with the latest trends with Exclusive & Advanced Knowledge and Training. \r\nIn her 12 yrs as a Stylist, Karlene has worked in different Salons but as with any career, the more people you work with the more you learn. \r\nKarlene has been lucky enough to work with some great talents in this industry and with every experience she walked away with greater knowledge and sharper skills.\r\nAfter working for others for years, She then decided it was time to become her own boss and realized that it was time to move forward and open her own Salon and then that’s when the the doors of Rendezvous Hair & Beauty opened. </div>[/four_fifth_last]</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[four_fifth]<div style="text-align: left;">Meet Sarah - Sarah has been a stylist for 8 years now and prides herself on making her clients feel renewed and refreshed after every salon experience. \r\n\r\nShe focuses on every detail to create a polished, fresh look for her clients. She continues to create cutting edge styles by advancing her Talent and knowledge when ever she is able. \r\n\r\nPerfection is Sarah''s only acceptable standard when it comes to hairdressing. She will undoubtedly accomplish any look you are going for. So, whether you’re looking for soft and sleek or bold and brilliant, Sarah is the stylist you want by your side.</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Sarah.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">[one_fifth]<img src="../images/stylists/Danielle.jpg" alt="">[/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]<div class="leftAligned">Meet Danielle - Danielle brings a positive upbeat attitude to the salon and is excellent with all hair types and styles for both men and women. She is consistently striving to exceed the customer’s expectations while making them feel comfortable in her chair. \r\n\r\nDanielle is truly passionate about hair and is always on top of the trends. It’s her personal goal to continue to grow and excel in her craft and to ultimately share all that she learned with her Clients. \r\n\r\nShe stays updated on all the latest trends and places high value on listening and understanding her client’s needs.\r\nShe is extremely passionate about making your hair it’s most fabulous, and prides herself in outstanding customer service. She specializes in colour, and just loves when someone wants a change. \r\n\r\nWhether you are looking for a great cut and color, or need the perfect look for your wedding, formal, or special occasion, you are sure to fall in love with your hair! Danielle would love to meet with you and she promises to make you love your hair again and again. </div>[/four_fifth_last]</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[four_fifth]<div style="text-align: left;">We would like to introduce our newest Member to our Team, Scarlett!!\r\n\r\nScarlett is very excited to join Karlene and her wonderful team at Rendezvous Hair and Beauty.\r\n\r\nAlong with being a very bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, Scarlett truly loves every aspect of hairdressing, but her speciality lies in Beautiful Blondes.\r\n\r\nScarlett thrives to give guests the best experience and make sure they feel welcome in the salon and not only communicate, but also educate on products and how to look after your hair at home. \r\n\r\nShe looks forward to meeting all of you and welcomes any of her current clients to our prestige boutique salon. \r\n\r\nWelcome Scarlett!</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Scarlett.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">[one_fifth]<img src="../images/stylists/Monique.jpg" alt="">[/one_fifth][four_fifth_last]<div class="leftAligned">We would like to Welcome Monique to our wonderful Team here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty.\r\n\r\nMonique is very passionate about her Clients, she strives to make sure each and every one is extremely well looked after and makes sure that her guests are very pleased with the end result of their hair but can also maintain and upkeep their amazing new look with ease.\r\nMonique understands how important it is to have a connection with your stylist so you are able to come in for a pleasant and easy to communicate appointment, as she knows how scary it can be to find that "perfect" stylist. \r\n\r\nMonique enjoys every aspect of hairdressing there is nothing she won''t strive to achieve "perfection only" when it come to your hair.\r\n\r\nWe welcome all Past clients of Monique''s to come and enjoy your time here at Rendezvous Hair & Beauty. </div>[/four_fifth_last]</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n[four_fifth]<div style="text-align: left;">The warmest welcomes to Shari!\r\n\r\nShari is a bubbly, friendly and easy to talk to stylist, She enjoys to for fill every clients needs and make them feel absolutely beautiful when they leave her chair.\r\n\r\nShari can provide you with up keep information and also easy styling techniques for home. \r\n\r\nShe thrives to give all clients the best experience in salon, help educate you on products and styling with what struggles you may have. \r\n\r\nShari looks forward to meeting new clients and welcomes back any of her past clientele and making you feel special and relaxed\r\nWelcome Scarlett!</div>[/four_fifth][one_fifth_last]<img src="../images/stylists/Shari.jpg" alt="stylist" class="leftAligned">[/one_fifth_last]\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Stylists', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-09 04:11:50', '2016-05-09 04:11:50', '', 40, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2016/05/09/40-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
